('9.117', 'Providing  and  fixing  factory  made  uPVC  door  frame  made  of  uPVC extruded sections having an overall dimension as below (tolerance ±1mm), with wall thickness  2.0 mm  (± 0.2 mm),  corners of the door  frame  to be Jointed with galvanized brackets  and stainless steel screws,  joints mitred and  plastic   welded.  The  hinge  side  vertical  of  the  frames  reinforced  by galvanized  M.S.  tube  of  size  19  X  19  mm  and  1  mm  (±  0.1  mm)  wall thickness and 3 nos. stainless steel hinges fixed to the frame complete as per manufacturer’s specification and direction of Engineer-in-charge', '', 0, 1037),
